Package diewald_CV_kit.blobdetection

Interface Summary
BLOBable the interface Blobable can be seen as a "function pointer".
 

Class Summary
Blob the class Blob represents the blobs/labels/regions found in an image.
BlobDetector BlobDetector is the main entry class of the library.
Contour the class Contour calculates a closed polyline of a blob.
Pixel the class Pixel is used for saving pixel coordinates, id-labeling (connected component labeling).
PixelRow used for calculating the blobs.
